Name: Magic Corgi
About the game: Your main character is a fluffy corgi dog and you have an exciting journey in a magical forest. Explore different levels, look for items and dodge various obstacles. How to manage? It's simple - pull the dog by the tail and fly in the right direction. Magic Corgi - 2D arcade game. A precision platformer in which it is worth trying to complete each of the 10 levels, because all of them are stuffed with various obstacles that can injure a harmless dog! Game Features: - exciting process - good physics - colorful graphics
